<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ELEARNING ACTIVATION EMAIL</title>
  <style type="/text.css">
    /* Base */
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }
      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        margin-top: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      /*layout*/
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-footer {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to FoodMat</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thanks for registering with FoodMat. Use this code to activate your account:</p>
      <h2> <%= activationCode %></h2>
      <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minute</p>
      <p>If you did not register to FootMat, ignore this email</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any question, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:support@bmat.com">support@bmat.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>